{"tid":2326601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴西衞生當局指中共不透明 拒絕授權緊急使用中共疫苗","createTime":"2020-12-15T12:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T16:40:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90438b0831436501dcaed524c8c14748a2da7819","tid":2326601,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"巴西衞生當局指中方不透明 不授權緊急使用中國疫苗<br />\n<br />\n巴西國家衞生監督局指，中國衛生當局透明度不足，不授權中國製造的新型冠狀病毒疫苗在巴西緊急使用。<br />\n<br />\n巴西目前的確診病例超過692萬宗，是全球第3多，僅次於美國及印度，但高層對是否對緊急應用中國疫苗，則趨於政治化，總統博爾索納羅一直質疑科興生物疫苗，而博爾索納羅的政敵、聖保羅州長多利亞就表示，打算在下月向當地居民接種科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2370784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2370784&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=69cdab42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2370784</a>"},{"pid":"01c99517eb6dc6ddac9cf0b9c874d2f92e28bd01","tid":2326601,"uid":126382,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"之前就俾支那係度試，試完又突然話唔俾用<br />\n<br />\n支那做咗啲嘢得罪人"},{"pid":"e24ca28e41cc7cd7238a2d11a8d6b2a03f4896d6","tid":2326601,"uid":258948,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UgmGb46.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgmGb46.gif&h=40a73285&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4b3c3418c5cfdc899ff6286a85bb3ba7463341d","tid":2326601,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"唔打大陸針呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914ed5b3c01f83935452e90ceebdf0e7fe0e93e8","tid":2326601,"uid":21171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01c99517eb6dc6ddac9cf0b9c874d2f92e28bd01","tid":2326601,"uid":126382,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"之前就俾支那係度試，試完又突然